**<u>ABSTRACT</u>**

This project is a full-stack Resume Builder web application designed to streamline the process of creating, editing, and managing professional resumes. The backend, built with Node.js and Express, provides robust APIs for user authentication, resume data management, and secure file uploads. It leverages a modular architecture with dedicated controllers, middleware, and MongoDB models to ensure scalability and maintainability. 

The frontend, developed using React and Vite, offers an intuitive and interactive user interface. Users can register, log in, and utilize a step-by-step form to input their personal, educational, and professional information. The application features multiple resume templates, real-time previews, and the ability to upload profile photos and other assets. State management and context are used to provide a seamless user experience, while Tailwind CSS ensures a modern and responsive design. 

Overall, this project empowers users to efficiently build and customize resumes, enhancing their job application process with a user-friendly and visually appealing platform.
